---
title: Sage & Garlicky Chicken with Creamy Bacon Potato Salad & Pear Salad
description: Herbs and garlic, no matchmaker can beat this legendary pair. Fragrant sage lights up the table with sensational aromas and the garlic seasoning adds a bit of bite to the chicken. Bacon and potato join together to create a creamy tartare potato salad. It’s a perfect match!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/sage-garlicky-chicken-d51ee1e3.jpg
